title: Shark Tank Season 1-7 (HDTV)(Scene)(Seedbox)
description:
Please enjoy this collection of all the HDTV scene releases of Shark Tank so far (including season 7). 

It took some work to find all the original encodes, and not crappy homemade reencodes. A good HDTV encode of S06E15 didn't exist, so I had to make my own from the 720p release.

BTW, in the middle of season 3 you see the scene transition from Xvid to x264, and with S07E23 their transition from MP4 to MKV.

I'm seeding this with my seedbox.

Enjoy, comment and share!
